This project aim at providing a fun approach to AGILE with the use of a mobile game.

The goal of this game is to produce an app by recruiting programmers with specifics skills.
A complete manual can be found on the "report.pdf" file.

This project is not ready to be published on Google Store but it is yet playable, a first APK is available in the app folder.


This project is protected by the AGPL license in version 3.0. A copy of the license is provided with this project in agpl-3.0.txt.

Special Thanks go to :
Laurent Mathy and Tom Barbette(@tbarbette) : for the course on Mobile Programming at University of Liege
Ivan Zarea (@minivan) : for his course on Agile Methodologies at Technical University of Chisinau
